" island girl " is a song performed by elton john that went to number one for three weeks on the billboard hot 100 in the u.s."weekly billboard hot 100 no . 1 songs from the first 50 years " , billboard.com . 2008 . and number 14 in the uk in 1975 .

lyricists : bernie taupin co - wrote many of this singer 's hits including " island girl " & " bennie and the jets "

